df = pd.read_json(first(path.rglob("images/*.json")))
df.pub_date = pd.to_datetime(df.pub_date)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
valid, train = train_test_split(df.copy(),train_size=0.4, stratify=df.pub_date.dt.year)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
train['is_valid'] = False
valid['is_valid'] = True
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
df = pd.concat([train,valid])
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
df.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
full_data = DataBlock(blocks=(ImageBlock, CategoryBlock),
                   splitter=ColSplitter(),
                   get_x=ColReader('download_image_path', pref=path/"images/"),
                   get_y=ColReader('label'),
                   item_tfms=Resize((1024), ResizeMethod.Squish),
                  batch_tfms=[*aug_transforms(size=(430,256),max_rotate=.01, max_warp=0.0), Normalize.from_stats(*imagenet_stats)])
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
dls = full_data.dataloaders(df, bs=32, num_workers=2)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
dls.show_batch()
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
metrics = [F1Score(average='weighted'), Precision(), Recall(), accuracy]
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
learn = cnn_learner(dls, squeezenet1_0,loss_func=LabelSmoothingCrossEntropy(), metrics=metrics)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
min, steep = learn.lr_find()
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
learn.fine_tune(30, base_lr=1e-2,
                cbs=[EarlyStoppingCallback(monitor='f1_score', patience=5),
                     ReduceLROnPlateau(monitor='f1_score',patience=4),
                     SaveModelCallback(monitor='f1_score'),
                     MixUp()])
